name: SCOUT - S1 in vortex
description:
The mandates I have left behind have helped me reflect on many things and learn new lessons. 
I have come to know several planets in different galaxies. Lonely places where there were only dust storms, others where only the harmony of nature existed. I found inhabitants of different races looking for a safe existence, others searching for precious materials hidden in space. Now I am passing through the vortex of time.
